snippet.title: The Sims™ 4 Moschino Stuff Pack: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Dress Sims in the latest Moschino Capsule Collection, inspired by The Sims as well as classic Moschino fashion! Then, start a career as a freelance fashion photographer and decorate a photo studio.

Available August 13, 2019 on PC and Mac and September 3, 2019 on PS4 and Xbox One. 

Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://x.ea.com/58898

#sims4
